    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_69",
      "heading": "2.  In this Act—",
      "content": "2.  In this Act—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_70",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“Minister”, in relation to a statutory body, means the Minister for the",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_71",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "time being responsible for the statutory body;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_72",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“Statutory body” means any body corporate, irrespective of the name \nby which it is known, that is incorporated pursuant to the provisions of \nfederal law and is a public authority or an agency of the Government \nof Malaysia but does not include a local authority and a body corporate \nthat is incorporated under the Companies Act 1965 [Act 125].",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_73",
      "heading": "PART II",
      "content": "PART II",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_74",
      "heading": "APPLICATION AND CONSTRUCTION",
      "content": "APPLICATION AND CONSTRUCTION",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_75",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Provisions of Act to apply to all statutory bodies",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_76",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "3.  The  provisions  of  this  Act  shall  apply  in  respect  of  all  statutory \nbodies  and  shall  be  read  together  and  construed  as  one  with  the \nprovisions  of  the  federal  law  pursuant  to  which  a  statutory  body  is \nincorporated.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_77",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Provisions  of  Act  to  supersede  conflicting  or \nprovisions of other federal law",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_78",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "inconsistent",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_79",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "4.  (1)  In  the  event  of  any  conflict  or  inconsistency  between  the \nprovisions  of  this  Act  and  of  the  federal  law  pursuant  to  which  a \nstatutory  body  is  incorporated,  the  provisions  of  this  Act  shall \nsupersede the conflicting or inconsistent provisions of that federal law \nand the latter shall be construed as so superseded.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_80",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)  The provisions of any  federal  law which are not in conflict or \ninconsistent with the provisions of this Act shall otherwise continue to \napply.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
