      "heading": "",
      "content": "Statutory Bodies (Account and Annual Reports)                 9",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_107",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "on or before 31 December 1980—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_108",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(a)  caused its statement of accounts to be audited; or",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_109",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(b)  prepared the annual report of its activities, in accordance with \nthe  provisions  of  the  federal  law  pursuant  to  which  it  is \nincorporated,  such  statutory  body  shall,  on  or  before  \n31 December 1981, cause its accounts to be audited and shall \nprepare the annual report of its activities in accordance with \nthe provisions of such federal law.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_110",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)  The provisions of sections 7 and 8—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_111",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(a)  shall  then  apply  in  respect  of  such  audited  statement  of",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_112",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "accounts and annual report of activities; and",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_113",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(b)  shall also apply in respect of other statements of accounts and \nannual  reports of activities of a statutory body in respect of \nfinancial years ending on or before 31 December 1980 which \nhave been audited and prepared, as the case may be, prior to \nthe date of publication of this Act in the Gazette but which \nhave not, on such date, been submitted to the Minister or laid \non  the  table  of  either  or  both  Houses  of  Parliament  in \naccordance with the provisions of the federal law pursuant to \nwhich the statutory body concerned is incorporated.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_114",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Minister may make rules",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_115",
      "heading": "11.  (1)  The Minister may make rules for the purpose of carrying \nout or giving effect to any of the provisions of this Act.",
      "content": "11.  (1)  The Minister may make rules for the purpose of carrying \nout or giving effect to any of the provisions of this Act.",
