      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_116",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)  In particular and without prejudice to the generality of the",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_117",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "power conferred by subsection (1), such rules may—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_118",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(a)  provide for the powers, functions, duties and responsibilities \nof  members  of  the  board  of  management  and  officers  and \nservants of  a statutory  body  in relation to the accounts and \nother records of the operations of that statutory body; and",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_119",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "10                                     Laws of Malaysia                            ACT 240",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_120",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(b)  prescribe  guidelines",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
